				<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Jonathan Marks, who attended Supernova 2004 from the Netherlands (and will be joining us again <a href="http://www.supernova2005.com">this year</a>), put together a fantastic short video with highlights from last year&#8217;s conference.</p>
<p>The video gives you a bit of the flavor of the event. And the fact that Jonathan put this together on his own gives you the flavor of the kind of people who attend. I like to say, &#8220;There is no audience at Supernova; only participants.&#8221; This is a perfect example.</p>
<p>Check the video out here: (<a href="http://www.supernova2005.com/downloads/supernova1.mov">Quicktime</a> | <a href="http://www.supernova2005.com/downloads/supernova2005.wmv">Windows Media</a>)</p>
